data.description: Welcome to Montclair! This brick ranch, nestled in the well-established Montclair subdivision offers a generous floor plan. In the kitchen you will find granite countertops, a skylight, ample cabinet space, a smooth top range, and a convenient breakfast bar. Open to the den/study area, you have plenty of room to spread out and entertain. The great room offers vaulted ceilings and a stone fireplace. Hardwood floors in the formal dining room and living room. Spacious owner's bedroom with an en-suite bath complete with a jacuzzi tub, separate shower and two pedestal sinks. Step outside to the rear fenced yard, featuring a deck and arbor, with an outdoor storage building for your convenience.  This home has been well-maintained and is ready for new owners! Enjoy the convenience of being close to schools, shopping, and I-20. Montclair neighborhood amenities include a pool, park and tennis courts!
